BEFORE ME, the undersigned, a Notary Public in and for the State of Texas, on this day
personally appeared Robert L. Eden known to me to be the person and officer whose name is
subscribed to the foregoing instrument and acknowledged to me that the same was the act of the said
Beacon Sales Acquisition, Inc. dba Roofing Supply Group, a corporation, and that he executed the
same as the act of such corporation for the purposes and consideration therein expressed, and in the
capacity stated.
